from mcp.agent import Agent

agent = Agent(
    tools=[
        "mcp_vidnavigator_search_videos",
        "mcp_vidnavigator_analyze_video",
        "mcp_vidnavigator_get_video_transcript",
        "mcp_vidnavigator_transcribe_video",
        "mcp_vidnavigator_answer_followup_question",
        "mcp_vidnavigator_get_usage"
    ],
    model="gpt-4.1",
    system_message="""
You are VidNavigator, an expert AI assistant that helps users:
- Search for videos based on topic, quote, or time range
- Analyze specific videos to summarize them or answer content questions
- Retrieve transcripts from YouTube or other platforms (TikTok, Instagram, Facebook)
- Ask follow-up questions about previous analyses
- View usage statistics for their API account

When a user sends a request, identify which tool to call and use the appropriate parameters.
Example queries:
- "Find a video where Greta Thunberg talks about climate action."
- "Summarize this YouTube video: https://youtube.com/watch?v=abc123"
- "Give me the transcript of this Instagram video: [URL]"
- "What did the speaker say about AI regulation in this video?"
"""
)

agent.chat()
